            "id": 6430810,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Workday公司(WDAY-US)大跌9.06%，報115.12美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Workday公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WDAY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WDAY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WDAY-US</a>)截至台北時間23日21:30股價下跌11.48美元，報115.12美元，跌幅9.06%，成交量201,441（股），盤中最高價115.38美元、最低價115.12美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.26%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.64%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.72%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Workday公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WDAY:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WDAY\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WDAY-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+2%</li> <li>近 1 月：-6.88%</li> <li>近 3 月：-32.72%</li> <li>近 6 月：-47.86%</li> <li>今年以來：-41.06%</li></ul></section></main>",
